.: Entry point for pull request management via the GitHub CLI. Handles common PR inspection and routes write operations to sub-skills, gh cli pr, gh cli pr skill, gh cli pr workflow
gh-cli-pr-comments: Add, edit, delete general pull request comments via GitHub CLI, gh cli pr comments, gh cli pr comments skill, gh cli pr comments workflow
gh-cli-pr-create: Open pull request via GitHub CLI, gh cli pr create, gh cli pr create skill, gh cli pr create workflow
gh-cli-pr-inline-comment/: Post, edit, or delete inline code review comments on PR diff lines. Routes to sub-skills by operation, gh cli pr inline comment, gh cli pr inline comment skill, gh cli pr inline comment workflow
gh-cli-pr-merge: Merge, update, revert, close pull request via GitHub CLI, gh cli pr merge, gh cli pr merge skill, gh cli pr merge workflow
gh-cli-pr-review: Approve, request changes on, dismiss pull request review via GitHub CLI, gh cli pr review, gh cli pr review skill, gh cli pr review workflow
gh-cli-pr-file-viewed: Mark or unmark one, multiple, or all files in a pull request as viewed via GitHub CLI, gh cli pr file viewed, gh cli pr mark file viewed, gh cli pr file viewed skill
